      "text": "ⅢXのセンター、franです\nよろしくお願いいたします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m IIIX’s center‚ fran.\nNice to meet you all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "もう。franちゃん、いっつもかたいんだから～\nもっとフランクでいいと思うよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran‚ you are always so formal~\nI’m sure you can be more candid with them~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、kanaって言います！\nって、もう知ってくれてます？　きゃはっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I’m kana!\nWait‚ do you already know that? Tee-hee!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "kanaったら……\n申し遅れました、mihoと申します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ kana…\nSorry for the late introductions. I’m miho.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
