      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ど、どうもご丁寧に……\n星見プロダクションの{user}です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ h-hi. Nice to meet you all.\nI’m {user} from Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 64.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……星見、プロダクション？\nてことは、そこにいる人達って？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Hoshimi Productions?\nSo that means the girls with you are…",
        "id": ""
