      "text": "長瀬……そう\n貴方があの、長瀬麻奈……さんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagase… I see.\nSo you’re… Mana Nagase…san’s…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 105.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "先日のNEXT VENUSグランプリ、拝見しました\n驚きましたよ、まさかダブル優勝を飾るなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We saw you perform at the last NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.\nWe were quite surprised to see a double-win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "今度のI-UNITYにも出場されるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you going to compete in the upcoming I-UNITY as well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 118.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
