      "text": "わぁ～一緒だ！　今日ライブを観てどうでした？\n私達に勝てそうですか？　なーんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oooh! Same! What’d ya think of the live today?\nThink you can beat us? Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
