      "text": "ふふ……頑張って下さい。でも勝つ気なら\n精一杯じゃ足りない。死ぬ気で来て下さいね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… Yes‚ please do. But if you want to win‚\nyour “best” won’t be enough. It’s a fight to the death. Got it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 143.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "死……、え……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Death… Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 147.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
